# Developer files are off limits

- Do **not** read, search, grep, or @-mention any file under `.developer_files/`.
- Do **not** run terminal commands to access `.developer_files/` (e.g. `cat`, `grep`, `php .developer_files/...`).
- If a task seems to require those files, ask the user instead of accessing them.
- These are local-only utilities (e.g. password helpers); the app does not depend on them.